        <num>9-15-4</num>
        <content>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1890-91, p. 100, § 1; Civil Code 1895, § 5398; Civil Code 1910, § 5986; Code 1933, § 24-3406; Ga. L. 1945, p. 207, § 1; Ga. L. 1957, p. 405, § 2; Ga. L. 1958, p. 398, § 1; Ga. L. 1970, p. 497, § 4; Ga. L. 1971, p. 214, § 2; Ga. L. 1972, p. 664, § 5; Ga. L. 1981, p. 1396, § 2; Ga. L. 1986, p. 1002, § 4; Ga. L. 1991, p. 1051, § 2; Ga. L. 2019, p. 683, § 1/HB 288.)</p>
          <p>The 2019 amendment,
      effective January 1, 2020, in subsection (a), deleted "and Code Section 15-6-77.2" following "15-6-77" in the first sentence and deleted "his" following "because of" in the middle of the second sentence.</p>
